::Cygnar::
       He receives a brief automated signal from his base.  He grimaces and 
curses at himself for not having expected it.  "They have already moved 
first.  My base is gone.  Destroyed by it's own self destruct.  I should've 
seen that coming."  He shakes his head and looks at Tyrael.  "They will 
attack you next.  The Maximal's are going to be their last target.  I 
recommend meeting them between your base and theirs.  Unless..."  He stares 
intently at Tyrael.  "How attached are you to your base?"

--part1_79.7b3a92.2ae75b83_boundary
